Module org.eclipse.persistence.core
Package org.eclipse.persistence.mappings.querykeys

Class QueryKey

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.mappings.querykeys.QueryKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
DirectQueryKey, ForeignReferenceQueryKey
public class QueryKey extends Object implements Cloneable, Serializable

Purpose: Define a Java appropriate alias to a database field or function.

Responsibilities:

  • Define the name of the alias.
  • Define the descriptor of the alias.
